  <div class="container" id="about-container">



   <p>The more time you spend researching and speaking with professionals in your chosen field, the better chance you will have in uncovering an amazing career opportunity. You will save time and frustration by avoiding areas of Finance that don’t match your skill set or interest you and you will greatly increase your chances of being selected during the interview process. Knowledge about the role and industry you are entering is a very powerful resource.This is not an opportunity to ask for a job. This is an opportunity to network with working professionals to find out more about the people and opportunities in different areas of finance. Please respect the privacy and time of the busy professionals in the Network.</p>
   <p>We have represented the Finance Industry in this format knowing that job titles, roles, and locations are subject to change and do not represent every option within Finance. Some companies have different titles and structures and may not match this exact configuration. Do not let that stop you from seeking information from our Network. If there is a specific role or area you would like to explore and we do not have anyone in the Network, please contact us and we will find you a connection.</p>
